     F** AAFRE9 *******************************************
     F* RETRIEVE THE TEXT OF CONTENTS FOR CHANGE          *
     F*      T.SAKASHITA                   2011.11.14     *
     F******************************************* AAFRE9 **
     FAAFPPE1 IF  E           K        DISK
      *
     C*P@RTN='0':OK
     C*P@RTN='1':NG
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P@HKBN  1
     C                     PARM           P@HENK 30
      *
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    P@HENK
      *
     C                     MOVEL'1'       P@RTN   1
      *
     C                     MOVELP@HKBN    K@HKBN  1
      *
     C           AAFKEY    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K@HKBN
      *
     C           AAFKEY    CHAINAAFPPE1              77
     C           *IN77     IFEQ '0'
     C           M@SKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C           M@SKHZ    ANDLE*DATE
     C                     SETON                     77
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C           *IN77     IFEQ '1'
     C                     GOTO @END
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVEL'0'       P@RTN
     C                     MOVELM@HENK    P@HENK
      *
     C           @END      TAG
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *
